  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.poster.avif?t=1712929771\" width=624 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.webm?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.mp4?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Last Sky is a narrative puzzle adventure about life, loss, and love. Through its meditative, dreamlike atmosphere you are invited to embark on a journey into Jake's mind, contemplating the opposites of life & death, fear & love, and loss & hope.<br><br>A visual odyssey about the beauty and sorrow of life, explore Jake's past, present, and future, as you progress through the mysterious multi-branching storyline. Enter a surreal dream world, where to overcome the past, Jake must reconnect with the present and the choices that you make will lead to one of several uniquely crafted endings.<br><br>The Last Sky combines 3D puzzles with 2D platforming inside a beautifully visualized world where the boundaries between dreams and reality dissolve as you become Jake's rudder in an uncharted ocean.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.poster.avif?t=1712929771\" width=624 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.webm?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.mp4?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.poster.avif?t=1712929771\" width=624 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.webm?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/44c324a5eddea61d0978174b38f79197.mp4?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Last Sky is a narrative puzzle adventure about life, loss, and love. Through its meditative, dreamlike atmosphere you are invited to embark on a journey into Jake's mind, contemplating the opposites of life & death, fear & love, and loss & hope.<br><br>A visual odyssey about the beauty and sorrow of life, explore Jake's past, present, and future, as you progress through the mysterious multi-branching storyline. Enter a surreal dream world, where to overcome the past, Jake must reconnect with the present and the choices that you make will lead to one of several uniquely crafted endings.<br><br>The Last Sky combines 3D puzzles with 2D platforming inside a beautifully visualized world where the boundaries between dreams and reality dissolve as you become Jake's rudder in an uncharted ocean.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.poster.avif?t=1712929771\" width=624 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.webm?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/536900/extras/e6b6ff0117b808d877b8e9e496bc8c8f.mp4?t=1712929771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
